  "titles": "Khenetai Occult Cabal",
  "lore": "The foremost warriors of the Khenetai formed cabals of ‘blades’, sublimely skilled warriors who had honed their psychic powers to be at one with their sword mastery. Their dual swords were shaped from single sheets of psychocrystalline infused ceramite and gilt, with sigils said to correspond to the wielder’s secret names and the deeds they had performed. In battle, the Khenetai fought with a unified precision that made them seem like a single warrior manifested many times, rather than a group of individual fighters.",
